Show list of files and more

A longer help can optionallly go here.

Usage:
  app dir
  app dir --all
  app dir DIR

Commands:
  dir
    Command description

Options:
  --all
    Also show hidden files

  -h --help
    Show this help

  --version
    Show version number

Parameters:
  DIR
    Directory to list

Environment Variables:
  SECRET
    There is no spoon

Examples:
  app dir
  app dir --all
